  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个用户旅程图，场景是员工在零售后台添加一个带多规格的新商品。整个流程要分四个阶段：进入网店、添加新产品、填写规格信息、最后完成提交。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Enter online shop",
        "Add new product",
        "Add variant (Retail_Inventory)",
        "Finish adding product"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。第一阶段是员工访问网站并登录，对吧？那登录之后，第二个阶段是不是直接点击\"添加商品\"和\"添加规格\"这两个操作？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Visit website somehow",
        "Log in as employee",
        "Click \"Add Product\"",
        "Click \"Add Variant\""
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，但第二阶段只到点击\"添加规格\"为止。真正的规格详情填写要放到第三个阶段，那个阶段会涉及零售库存系统（Retail_Inventory）和优惠券系统（Retail_CouponSystem）的字段。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Add variant (Retail_Inventory)",
        "Set current price (Retail_CouponSystem)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我在第三阶段画出了填写规格详情的步骤：填写名称、设置可见性、写描述、设定零售价，还有那个关联优惠券系统的当前价格字段。另外加上了上传图片。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Provide name",
        "Set visibility",
        "Write description",
        "Set retail price",
        "Set current price (Retail_CouponSystem)",
        "Add images"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，第三阶段的名字我想确认一下——括号里的系统标注是Retail_Inventory，但步骤里既有库存相关的价格，又有Retail_CouponSystem的价格。这样标注会不会让人误解？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Add variant (Retail_Inventory)",
        "Set current price (Retail_CouponSystem)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我理解您的顾虑。不过Retail_Inventory是主系统，优惠券价格只是其中一个字段的关联。我可以保持标题为\"Add variant (Retail_Inventory)\"，同时在步骤里明确标出Retail_CouponSystem的特殊性，这样主次清晰。您看可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Add variant (Retail_Inventory)",
        "Set current price (Retail_CouponSystem)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，这样处理合理。最后第四阶段就是收尾工作：选择默认规格、添加到分类，然后点击提交。整个旅程的参与者都是Employee，满意度评分都用4分，除了登录步骤用3分——因为登录体验还有优化空间。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Select default variant",
        "Add product to categories",
        "Click \"Submit\"",
        "Employee",
        "Log in as employee"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成了。整个旅程图标题是\"Adding a new product that has multiple variants\"，四个阶段、十三个步骤全部就位，评分和角色也按您说的设置好了。您检查一下有没有遗漏？",
